item.title: E516 - Spring 2020 Proceedings
item.description: Here you find the Documents produced by the students for this class. Please note that some may be edited by Gregor von Laszewski or the support staff for this class. We try to update this document frequently. The best we to read them is with an ePub reader. If you do not have one you also use the PDF version. However, PDF does not render as well as ePub.
